<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q9_v12" title="Q9_v12" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd"><qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"><qti-correct-response><qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value></qti-correct-response></qti-response-declaration><qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/><qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/><qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body><p>Por la mañana, una persona compra medio kilo de queso, tres cuartos de kilo de jamón y un cuarto de kilo de pan. Por la tarde, vuelve a la tienda y compra otro cuarto de kilo de queso, medio kilo de jamón y tres cuartos de kilo de pan. El queso cuesta $6000 el kilo, el jamón $5200 el kilo y el pan $1500 el kilo.</p><p>¿Cuál de las siguientes expresiones representa el gasto total de esa persona en queso, jamón y pan durante ese día?</p><qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1"><qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mtext>0,5+0,25</m:mtext><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>5200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mtext>0,75+0,5</m:mtext><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>6000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mtext>0,25+0,75</m:mtext><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>1500</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math><qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. En esta expresión se asigna <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>5200</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> al queso y <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>6000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> al jamón, pero el enunciado dice que el queso cuesta <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>6000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> por kilo y el jamón <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>5200</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Por ejemplo, el queso total es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>0,5</m:mtext><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mtext>0,25</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>0,75</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math> kg, así que su costo debe ser <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>0,75</m:mtext><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>6000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>4&#160;500</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, no <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>0,75</m:mtext><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>5200</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>3&#160;900</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice><qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mtext>0,5+0,25</m:mtext><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>6000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mtext>0,75+0,5</m:mtext><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>5200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mtext>0,25+0,75</m:mtext><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>1500</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math><qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! La expresión agrupa cada producto comprado en la mañana y en la tarde y lo multiplica por su precio por kilogramo: queso <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mtext>0,5</m:mtext><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mtext>0,25</m:mtext><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>6000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>0,75</m:mtext><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>6000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>4&#160;500</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, jamón <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mtext>0,75</m:mtext><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mtext>0,5</m:mtext><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>5200</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>1,25</m:mtext><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>5200</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>6&#160;500</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> y pan <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mtext>0,25</m:mtext><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mtext>0,75</m:mtext><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>1500</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>1500</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>1500</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. El gasto total es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>4&#160;500</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>6&#160;500</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>1500</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;500</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice><qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mtext>0,5+0,75</m:mtext><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>6000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mtext>0,25+0,5</m:mtext><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>5200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mtext>0,25+0,75</m:mtext><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>1500</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math><qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Aquí se suman cantidades que no corresponden al mismo producto. El queso comprado es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>0,5</m:mtext><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mtext>0,25</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>0,75</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math> kg, no <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>0,5</m:mtext><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mtext>0,75</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>1,25</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math> kg. El jamón comprado es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>0,75</m:mtext><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mtext>0,5</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>1,25</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math> kg, no <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>0,25</m:mtext><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mtext>0,5</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>0,75</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math> kg. Por eso la expresión no representa correctamente la compra del día.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice><qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mtext>0,5+0,25+0,75+0,5+0,25+0,75</m:mtext><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>6000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>5200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>1500</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math><qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Esta expresión multiplica la suma de todos los kilos por la suma de todos los precios por kilo, pero cada producto tiene un precio distinto. Por ejemplo, el total de kilos es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>0,5</m:mtext><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mtext>0,25</m:mtext><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mtext>0,75</m:mtext><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mtext>0,5</m:mtext><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mtext>0,25</m:mtext><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mtext>0,75</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, y la suma de precios es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>6000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>5200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>1500</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;700</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, de modo que da <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;700</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>38&#160;100</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, que no corresponde al gasto real. El gasto correcto es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;500</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice></qti-choice-interaction><qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show"><qti-content-body><p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p><ol><li><p><strong>Identificar cuánto se compra de cada producto en todo el día</strong></p><p>Queso:</p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>0,5</m:mtext><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mtext>0,25</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>0,75</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math><p>Jamón:</p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>0,75</m:mtext><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mtext>0,5</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>1,25</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math><p>Pan:</p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>0,25</m:mtext><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mtext>0,75</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></li><li><p><strong>Multiplicar cada cantidad total por su precio por kilogramo</strong></p><p>Queso:</p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>0,75</m:mtext><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>6000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4&#160;500</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math><p>Jamón:</p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>1,25</m:mtext><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>5200</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6&#160;500</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math><p>Pan:</p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>1500</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1500</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></li><li><p><strong>Sumar los tres gastos</strong></p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4&#160;500</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>6&#160;500</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1500</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;500</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math><p>El gasto total es $12 500.</p></li><li><p><strong>Escribir la expresión que representa ese cálculo</strong></p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mtext>0,5</m:mtext><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mtext>0,25</m:mtext><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>6000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mtext>0,75</m:mtext><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mtext>0,5</m:mtext><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>5200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mtext>0,25</m:mtext><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mtext>0,75</m:mtext><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>1500</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></li><li><p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p><p>La expresión correcta es la alternativa B.</p></li></ol></qti-content-body></qti-feedback-block></qti-item-body><qti-response-processing><qti-response-condition><qti-response-if><qti-match><qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/><qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value></qti-match><qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE"><qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value></qti-set-outcome-value><qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK"><qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value></qti-set-outcome-value><qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION"><qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value></qti-set-outcome-value></qti-response-if><qti-response-else-if><qti-match><qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/><qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value></qti-match><qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK"><qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value></qti-set-outcome-value><qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION"><qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value></qti-set-outcome-value></qti-response-else-if><qti-response-else-if><qti-match><qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/><qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value></qti-match><qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK"><qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value></qti-set-outcome-value><qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION"><qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value></qti-set-outcome-value></qti-response-else-if><qti-response-else-if><qti-match><qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/><qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value></qti-match><qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK"><qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value></qti-set-outcome-value><qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION"><qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value></qti-set-outcome-value></qti-response-else-if><qti-response-else><qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK"><qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value></qti-set-outcome-value><qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION"><qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value></qti-set-outcome-value></qti-response-else></qti-response-condition></qti-response-processing></qti-assessment-item>